20US%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20will%20continue%20over%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20an%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revamped%20Google%20Shopping%20provides%20users%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-overviews-search-engine-new-openai-searchgpt-competition-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGoogle%2527s%2520AI%2520Overviews%252C%2520which%2520are%2Ccited%2520information%2520throughout%2520the%2520response.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Overviews-like%20brief%20of%20the%20top%20things%20to%20consider%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20looking%20up%20a%20product%2C%20as%20well%20as%20recommendations.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20quick%20search%20of%20%26quot%3Bmen's%20winter%20jacket%20for%20Seattle%26quot%3B%20generates%20a%20response%20about%20factors%20to%20consider%20like%20water%20resistance%20or%20windproof%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20AI%20jacket%20search%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d78cca70318649281b6f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20Shopping%20now%20has%20AI%20Overviews-like%20briefing%20to%20provide%20more%20context%20to%20users%20on%20what%20they're%20looking%20to%20buy.%20%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20updated%20Google%20Shopping%20homepage%20features%20a%20personalized%20feed%20filled%20with%20shoppable%20products%20and%20videos%20based%20on%20your%20preferences.%20The%20shopping%20feed%20considers%20inputs%20from%20Google%20surfaces%20including%20your%20shopping%20activity%20on%20Chrome%2C%20Search%2C%20YouTube%20and%20Discover%2C%20a%20Google%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20allows%20you%20to%20pick%20up%20where%20you%20left%20off%20in%20your%20last%20shopping%20session%20after%20being%20away.%20Users%20can%20also%20turn%20off%20personalized%20results%20in%20their%20%26quo