3E%26quot%3BIt%20(EVM)%20has%20a%20single%20use%20battery%20which%20can%20be%20used%20for%205-7%20days.%20It's%20like%20a%20calculator%20battery.%20We%20have%20made%20a%20provision.%20It%20is%20initially%20marked%20as%20its%2099%20per%20cent%20and%20charged.%20It%20can%20differ%20based%20on%20difference%20of%20voltage.%20When%20it%20drops%20to%205.8%25%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20signal%20that%20it%20is%20about%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20underscoring%20that%20the%20system%20is%20foolproof%2C%20dismissing%20rumours%20that%20the%20machine%20can%20be%20hacked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batteries%20are%20put%20on%20the%20day%20the%20machines%20(EVMs)%20are%20commissioned%20and%20not%20before%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20EVMs%20are%20not%20connected%2C%20hence%20they%20can't%20be%20hacked%20into%2C%20said%20the%20top%20poll%20officer%20as%20he%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-to-vote-in-single-phase-on-nov-20-results-on-nov-23-6794297%5C%22%3Edates%20for%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20explained%20it%20many%20times.%20It%20will%20take%20time%20but%20let%20me%20explain%20again.%20Before%205-6%20months%20of%20polls%2C%20checking%20begins.%20At%20every%20step%20of%20EVM%20process%2C%20political%20parties%20or%20their%20agents%20are%20present.%20We%20put%20a%20new%20battery%20and%20after%20sealing%20there%20are%20signatures%20of%20the%20agent.%20There's%20a%20three-layer%20of%20security%20including%20CAPF%20and%20observers.%20The%20process%20is%20videographed.%20The%20EVM%20numbers%20are%20also%20shared.%20When%20polls%20are%20over%2C%20even%20then%20we%20take%20signatures.%20How%20much%20more%20can%20we%20show%3F%20On%20counting%20day%2C%20it%20goes%20inside%20barricading.%20There's%20a%20provision%20for%20objecting%20to%20any%20of%20this%20at%20any%20stage%20which%20has%20not%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20that%20the%20party%20had%20sent%20a%20list%20of%2020%20seats%20in%20which%20the%20candidates%20had%20submitted%20their%20written%20and%20verbal%20complaints%20over%20the%20EVM%20counting%20votes%20in%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20sent%20a%20list%20of%2020%20seats%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20regarding%20which%20our%20candidates%20have%20submitted%20written%20and%20verbal%20complaints%20of%2099%20per%20cent%20battery%20charge.%20This%20issue%20was%20raised%20on%20the%20day%20of%20counting...This%20is%20a%20strange%20coincidence%20that%20the%20machines%20which%20displayed%2099%20per%20cent%20battery%20charge%20were%20the%20ones%20on%20which%20Congress%20was%20mostly%20made%20to%20lose.%20The%20machines%20with%2060-70%20per%20cent%20battery%20charge%20are%20the%20ones%20on%20which%20Congress%20won.%20Why%20did%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khera%20speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20results%20over%20the%20last%2010-15%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20can't%20be%20that%20when%20results%20don't%20go%20your%20way%20you%20start%20raising%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EKitna%20dikhayenge%2C%20kaun%20dikhata%20hai%20itna%20bataiye.%20Koi%20ek%20process%20comparative%20bataiye%20poori%20country%20main%20jahan%20public%20disclosure%2C%20disclosure%2C%20disclosure%2C%20participation%2C%20participation%20itna%20adkhik%20ho.%20Koi%20ek%20bataiye%20process%3C%2Fem%3E%20(How%20much%20more%20transparent%20can%20we%20be%2C%20you%20tell%20me.%20Tell%20me%20about%20one%20comparative%20process%20where%20there%20is%20so%20much%20public%20disclosure%20and%20participation.%20You%20show%20me%20one%20process)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728996900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F91ehru5o_voting-