0this%20beforehand%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20a%20role%20until%20now.%20With%20the%20MCC%20in%20force%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20very%20strict%20view%20on%20this%20and%20we%20will%20direct%20everyone%20that%20violence%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20any%20crime%2C%20especially%20against%20a%20political%20person%2C%20should%20not%20happen%2C%20should%20not%20repeat.%20We%20have%20not%20allowed%20it%20to%20happen%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir...%20state%20after%20state.%20We%20are%20sure%20it%20will%20not%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique%2C%20who%20was%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20and%20a%20member%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20on%20Saturday%20night%20outside%20the%20Bandra%20East%20office%20of%20his%20son%20and%20MLA%20Zeeshan%20Siddique.%20Three%20attackers%20fired%20at%20least%20six%20bullets%2C%20four%20of%20which%20hit%20Baba%20Siddique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20attacked%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20BJP-NCP-Shiv%20Sena%20coalition%20over%20the%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20murder%2C%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20President%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20said%20people%20in%20the%20government%20should%20take%20responsibility%20and%20step%20down%20from%20their%20posts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20It%20is%20sad%20that%20former%20state%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%2C%20Mumbai.%20If%20the%20Home%20minister%20and%20the%20rulers%20will%20take%20the%20state's%20vehicle%20forward%20with%20such%20leniency%2C%20it%20can%20be%20a%20warning%20sign%20for%20the%20common%20people.%20This%20not%20only%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%2C%20the%20rulers%20need%20to%20accept%20responsibility%20and%20step%20down%20from%20their%20posts.%20My%20heartfelt%20tribute%20to%20Baba%20Siddiqui%20and%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20Marathi%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Shinde%20said%20law%20and%20order%20had%20deteriorated%20under%20the%20alliance%20led%20by%20the%20opposition%20coalition%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20and%20promised%20that%20the%20people%20responsible%20for%20Siddique's%20killing%20would%20not%20be%20spared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20in%20all%20288%20Assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20cast%20their%20ballots%20on%20November%2020.%20Counting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728996600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fk9lllno8_rajiv-kumar_625x300_15_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-murder-maharashtra-elections-rajiv-kumar-violence-no-go-area-poll-body-chief-on-baba-siddique-murder-6795454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allaying%20fears%20over%20%26quot%3Blaw%20and%20order%20issues%26quot%3B%20affecting%20voting%20after%20last%20week's%20killing%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20said%20it%20will%20be%20made%20very%20clear%20to%20the%20authorities%20that%20violence%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bno-go%20area%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DP-Ranveer%20in%20new%20ad%3B%20fans%20ask%20their%20baby's%20name%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728996579000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114253440%2Cimgsize-48972.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffans-smitten-by-ranveer-singh-and-deepika-padukones-new-ad-ask-them-to-revea