0Branch%20because%20they're%20one%20of%20just%20a%20few%20companies%20that%20offer%20a%20standing%20desk%20suitable%20for%20small%20spaces.%20It's%20also%20a%20highly-rated%20brand%E2%80%94its%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-ergonomic-chair%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ergonomic%20office%20chair%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20best%20you%20could%20buy%20for%20its%20adjustable%20design%2C%20and%20I%20was%20expecting%20the%20same%20out%20of%20the%20standing%20desk.%20The%20Duo%20Standing%20Desk%20is%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20use%20and%20moves%20seamlessly%20to%20reach%20the%20exact%20right%20height%2C%20whether%20sitting%20or%20standing.%20Since%20introducing%20a%20standing%20desk%20into%20my%20workday%2C%20not%20only%20have%20I%20been%20more%20comfortable%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20more%20productive%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220d886a5-7970-4159-b656-63419bfc56b0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22branch%20standing%20desk%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d6382a70318649281af97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Branch%20Duo%20has%20a%20sleek%20modern%20design.%20Users%20can%20choose%20from%20five%20top%20styles%20and%20three%20frame%20colors%2C%20with%20the%20option%20to%20add%20optional%20accessories%20like%20a%20drawer%2C%20cable%20organizer%2C%20or%20privacy%20panel.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3Dd5accbc958716fd9469e908d206d2a6b7e3ff6935d98b88e50c5fcd674f78381%26postID%3D670d5f870c43543ec7b95042%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbranch-duo-standing-desk-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.branchfurniture.com%252Fproducts%252Fduo-standing-desk%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBranch%20Duo%20Standing%20Desk%3C%2Fa%3E%20features%20a%20sleek%20modern%20design%3B%20the%20base%20and%20tabletop%20can%20be%20customized%20to%20your%20needs.%20The%20legs%20are%20made%20out%20of%20a%20strong%2C%20sturdy%20metal%20and%20come%20in%20three%20different%20colors%3A%20white%2C%20charcoal%2C%20or%20a%20trendy%20sage%20green.%20I'd%20recommend%20starting%20with%20your%20base%20and%20then%20selecting%20a%20top.%20There%20are%20five%20top%20styles%2C%20ranging%20from%20matching%20solid%20colors%20for%20a%20monochromatic%20desk%20or%20wood%20tones%20including%20woodgrain%20or%20walnut%2C%20all%20made%20from%20MDF.%20I%20went%20with%20a%20white%20base%20and%20woodgrain%20top%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20perfect%20light%20neutral.%20This%20desk%20is%20available%20in%20three%20different%20sizes%3A%2036%20x%2024%20inches%2C%2048%20x%2024%20inches%2C%20and%20a%20recently%20added%2058%20x%2027%20inches.%20I%20chose%20the%20smallest%20option%20to%20best%20fit%20into%20my%20500-square-foot%20New%20York%20City%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20desk%20is%20pretty%20minimalist%20overall%2C%20with%20wide%20frame%20legs%20and%20a%20small%20notch%20to%20thread%20cables%20through%20in%20the%20back.%20Compared%20to%20other%20standing%20desks%2C%20its%20technical%20features%20feel%20more%20discreet%20%E2%80%94%20just%20one%20small%20adjustment%20panel%20on%20the%20front%20left%20corner.%20Living%20in%20a%20studio%20apartment%2C%20I%20appreciate%20this%2C%20since%20my%20furniture%20is%20always%20fully%20displayed.%20The%20edges%20of%20the%20desk's%20surface%20are%20rounded%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20touch%20if%2C%20like%20me%2C%20you%20sometimes%20bump%20into%20your%20furniture.%20Branch%20also%20offers%20a%20number%20of%20add-ons%20to%20enhance%20your%20workspace%2C%20such%20as%20a%20cable%20organizer%20and%20clamp-on%20power%20charger.%20I%20opted%20to%20add%20a%20drawer%2C%20which%20attaches%20right%20under%20the%20desk's%20center.%20The%20drawer%20glides%20open%20easily%20and%20is%20lined%20in%20felt%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20less%20noisy%20to%20use%20and%20keeps%20objects%20from%20sliding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22109c82a2-c0bf-4df5-a0e4-45419937fe49%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Branch%20Duo%20Standing%20Desk%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Branch%20Duo%20Standing%20Desk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20view%20of%20the%20branch%20duo%20desk%20at%20an%20angle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d6ad53f2165d716e0ae20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Branch%20Duo%20has%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20assemble%2C%20but%20you'll%20likely%20want%20a%20helping%20hand.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c9f6d8b-eea5-47e8-81c3-ff631798fee1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Duo%20Standing%20Desk%20shipped%20quickly%20and%20arrived%20at%20my%20door%20in%20two%20boxes%3A%20one%20for%20the%20tabletop%20and%20one%20for%20the%20legs%20and%20drawer.%20The%20desk%20weighs%20about%2065%20pounds%2C%20and%20the%20boxes%20were%20heavy%20but%20manageable%20to%20move%20from%20my%20building%20lobby%20to%20my%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20the%20best%20at%20assembling%20furniture%2C%20so%20I%20enlisted%20my%20dad%20to%20help.%20Overall%2C%20the%20desk%20was%20pretty%20straightforward%20to%20set%20up%20with%20the%20instruction%20manual.%20The%20top%20attaches%20to%20the%20legs%3B%20and%20all%20the%20holes%20were%20pre-drilled%20to%20make%20the%20process%20seamless.%20The%20trickiest%20part%20of%20assembly%20was%20securing%20the%20wiring%20underneath%20the%20desk%20with%20cable%20clips.%20My%20dad%20and%20I%20found%20that%20having%20two%20people%20made%20this%20step%20easier%20because%20I%20could%20hold%20the%20wires%20in%20the%20right%20spot%20to%20ensure%20they%20didn't%20move%20around.%20It%20also%20made%20sense%20to%20attach%20the%20drawer%20last%20(although%20the%20brand%20said%20to%20do%20so%20sooner)%20so%20that%20it%20didn't%20interfere%20with%20the%20wiring.%20You'll%20likely%20also%20need%20two%20people%20to%20flip%20the%20assembled%20desk%20right-side%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20drawer%20with%20felt%20liner%20on%20the%20branch%20duo%20standing%20desk%20with%20various%20cords%2C%20a%20screwdriver%2C%20and%20other%20small%20items%20inside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d63823f2165d716e0aaa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20added%20a%20small%20drawer%20that%20was%20lined%20with%20felt%20to%20keep%20small%20items%20from%20rolling%20around.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Branch%20website%2C%20the%20brand%20boasts%20its%20desk%20can%20be%20assembled%20within%20your%20lunch%20break.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20typical%20assembly%20process%2C%20this%20wasn't%20exactly%20the%20case%20for%20us%2C%20unless%20of%20course%2C%20you%20take%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20long%20lunch%20breaks.%20Most%20of%20the%20screws%20need%20to%20be%20secured%20using%20a%20basic%20Allen%20wrench%2C%20which%20came%20with%20the%20desk.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20slow%20and%20tedious%20process%20and%20took%20us%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20total%20%E2%80%94%20however%2C%20setup%20can%20be%20sped%20up%20if%20you%20have%20your%20own%20wrench%20or%20power%20drill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22092bc5bf-8d46-4f76-af91-e13c4f53b1f1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20with%20the%20desk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20used%20a%20basic%20desk%20for%20my%20entire%2010-year%20career%20and%20have%20always%20worked%20while%20sitting%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20the%20Branch%20Duo%20to%20change%20my%20routine.%20However%2C%20it%20only%20took%20a%20few%20uses%20for%20me%20to%20start%20reaping%20its%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20first%20use%2C%20the%20desk%20is%20easy%20to%20adjust%2C%20with%20about%20a%2020-inch%20range%20of%20motion.%20The%20desk%20specs%20say%20the%20desk%20extends%20from%2028%20to%2047.5%20inches%2C%20though%20my%20desk%20went%20from%2027.8%20to%2047%20inches.%20The%20small%20control%20panel%20is%20key%20to%20using%20the%20desk's%20different%20features%2C%20including%20raising%20and%20lowering%20it.%20The%20screen%20generally%20stays%20black%2C%20which%20adds%20to%20the%20discreetness%20of%20the%20design%2C%20but%20when%20you%20hold%20it%20down%20or%20up%2C%20it%20shows%20the%20table's%20height%20down%20to%20the%20centimeter.%20You%20can%20also%20program%20two%20presets%20to%20auto-adjust%20to%20your%20preferred%20seating%20and%20standing%20heights.%20The%20handset%20can%20also%20remind%20you%20to%20stand%20up.%20You%20customize%20how%20often%20you%20want%20this%20reminder%2C%20and%20there's%20an%20option%20to%20add%20a%20vibration%20or%20not%2C%20which%20I%20appreciate%20as%20someone%20who%20can%20be%20sensitive%20to%20noises%20while%20working.%20Since%20the%20control%20panel%20screen%20stays%20black%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20I%20found%20the%20light-up%20reminder%20to%20be%20enough%20to%20capture%20my%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%20eight%20seconds%20to%20raise%2010%20inches%20and%20go%20from%20sitting%20to%20standing.%20The%20movement%20is%20quick%20and%20seamless.%20Since%20you%20have%20to%20actively%20push%20the%20button%20to%20adjust%20the%20desk%2C%20there's%20minimal%20risk%20of%20accidental%20movement.%20While%20the%20desk%20isn't%20noisy%20overall%2C%20it%20does%20make%20a%20noticeable%20sound%2C%20right%20about%2050%20decibels%2C%20while%20moving%20up%20and%20down.%20It%20sounds%20almost%20like%20a%20fan%20buzzing%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20loud%20enough%20to%20wake%20my%20sleeping%20dog%20up%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20my%20biggest%20concern%20while%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20the%20branch%20duo%20control%20panel%2C%20reads%2030.5%20inches%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d629b3f2165d716e0aa4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20discreet%20control%20panel%20displays%20the%20exact%20height%20of%20your%20desk%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20make%20two%20presets.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20that%20the%20control%20panel%20isn't%20overly%20technical-looking%2C%20but%20I%20will%20admit%20that%20it%20took%20me%20some%20time%20to%20learn%20to%20use%20it.%20It%20only%20has%20two%20buttons%20on%20either%20side.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20accidentally%20set%20the%20sedentary%20reminder%20and%20then%20struggled%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20turn%20it%20off.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20tuck%20my%20user%20guide%20into%20the%20desk%20drawer%20until%20muscle%20memory%20caught%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20short%20girl%2C%20I'm%20sometimes%20nervous%20about%20ordering%20products%20that%20are%20based%20on%20height.%20Luckily%2C%20this%20desk%20is%20petite-friendly%2C%20and%20the%20wide%20frame%20also%20gives%20my%20legs%20plenty%20of%20space%20while%20sitting.%20I'm%20exactly%20five%20feet%20tall%20and%20used%20it%20on%20the%20lower%20side%20of%20the%20height%20range%2C%20but%20it%20would%20accommodate%20taller%20users%20as%20well%2C%20up%20to%20about%20six-foot-one%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3Df8db54069223959ce83e6e01736f8c59a5ad00ea383e35d337477b7c86b44336%26postID%3D670d5f870c43543ec7b95042%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbranch-duo-standing-desk-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.branchfurniture.com%252Fpages%252Fergonomics-calculator%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBranch's%20ergonomics%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20desk%20can%20support%20up%20to%20275%20pounds%20and%20it%20felt%20sturdy%20at%20all%20heights%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20weight%20I%20put%20on%20it.%20Now%2C%20I%20don't%20tend%20to%20lean%20on%20my%20desk%20much%20while%20working%2C%20so%20to%20put%20this%20to%20the%20test%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20raising%20the%20desk%20up%20and%20down%20while%20sitting%20on%20it.%20Even%20at%20its%20tallest%20height%2C%20I%20felt%20secure%20with%20no%20shakes%20or%20wobbles.%20As%20a%20dog%20owner%2C%20I%20also%20appreciated%20having%20a%20surface%20that%20I%20could%20raise%20out%20of%20my%20dog's%20reach%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1b4fac5-136a-4109-8a63-05fedf35a8dc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20lives%20in%20a%20small%20apartment%2C%20I%20take%20organization%20seriously%20and%20tend%20to%20look%20for%20furniture%20that%20conceals%20clutter.%20The%20biggest%20downside%20of%20this%20desk%20for%20me%20is%20its%20lack%20of%20storage%2C%20a%20prevalent%20design%20flaw%20of%20most%20standing%20desks.%20Previously%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fp%2Flagkapten-alex-desk-black-brown-white-s59432163%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIkea%20Lagkapten%20Desk%20and%20Alex%20Drawers%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20double%20duty%20as%20a%20vanity%20too%2C%20and%20had%20lots%20of%20drawers%2C%20so%20this%20took%20getting%20used%20to.%20I'd%20recommend%20getting%20a%20separate%20drawer%20set%20for%20your%20home%20office%20if%20you%20need%20more%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20took%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to%20the%20control%20panel%20and%20setting%20up%20the%20tricky%20wiring.%20Luckily%20my%20dad%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20workaround%20for%20any%20difficulty%20we%20encountered%20during%20setup%2C%20but%20if%20I%20had%20been%20on%20my%20own%20for%20this%20process%2C%20I%20would%20have%20had%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20customer%20service.%20Once%20getting%20over%20the%20learning%20curve%20for%20the%20control%20panel%2C%20using%20this%20desk%20has%20been%20truly%20seamless.%20While%20its%20tabletop%20is%20more%20narrow%20than%20other%20options%2C%20it%20offers%20plenty%20of%20work%20space%2C%20and%20Branch%20makes%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3D441cea87abd712ac025892a7a55635359ed264ea385b8be12bbd23ae96ab9150%26postID%3D670d5f870c43543ec7b95042%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbranch-duo-standing-desk-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.branchfurniture.com%252Fcollections%252Fmonitor-and-laptop-stands%252Fproducts%252Fmonitor-arm%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompatible%20monitor%20arm%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20use%20a%20desktop.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291f97db1-7b34-4024-a64c-6db35245ad79%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBranch%20also%20offers%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56307-20%26h%3Dc4a66fca33fe0f43ea3012ccda6292f76119ffbbddb085cb2fc310ca75fb4cb4%26postID%3D670d5f870c43543ec7b95042%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbranch-duo-standing-desk-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.branchfurniture.com%252Fcollections%252Fdesks%252Fproducts%252Fstanding-desk%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanding%20Desk%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20might%20be%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20larger%20office%20spaces.%20Compared%20to%20the%20Branch%20Duo%2C%20it%20com