0what%20was%20the%20sample%20size%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-poll-body-to-announce-maharashtra-jharkhand-election-dates-today-maharashtra-elections-jharkhand-elections-elections-2024-6793634%5C%22%3Ethe%20Election%20Commission%20said%20today%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20announcing%20the%20poll%20dates%20for%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand.%20This%2C%20the%20Commission%20said%2C%20is%20an%20occasion%20where%20the%20media%20must%20introspect%20and%20correct%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20govern%20exit%20polls%20-%20but%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20introspect%20-%20what%20was%20the%20sample%20size%20etc.%20There%20are%20bodies%20that%20self-regulate.%20Time%20has%20come%20that%20the%20concerned%20bodies%20will%20do%20some%20self-regulation%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-to-vote-in-single-phase-on-nov-20-results-on-nov-23-6794297%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Eadded%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bgap%20between%20expectation%20and%20reality%20can%20lead%20to%20frustration%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20one%20cannot%20expect%20the%20trends%20to%20match%20the%20exit%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20he%20also%20clarified%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20trends%20announcements%2C%20which%20featured%20in%20the%20huge%20row%20during%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20from%20Haryana%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20lost%20the%20election%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20win%20comfortably%2C%20had%20complained%20that%20the%20time%20lag%20between%20the%20announcements%20and%20the%20live%20counting%20in%20progress%20at%20various%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20amplified%20the%20shock%20for%20the%20party%20was%20that%20it%20was%20ahead%20in%20the%20early%20trends%20before%20its%20score%20nosedived.%20The%2