remembers-co-star-atul-parchure-in-heartfelt-noteyou-will-forever-have-a-special-place-in-my-heart%2Farticleshow%2F114250650.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goldman%20Sachs%20beats%20Wall%20Street%20forecasts%20as%20investment-banking%20fees%20surge%2020%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Solomon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e30dba70318649281c74b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20praised%20the%20bank's%20strong%20performance%20in%20its%20third-quarter%20earnings.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FDanny%20Moloshok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20reported%20third-quarter%20earnings%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20beat%20analysts'%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20investment%20bank%20posted%20%2412.7%20billion%20of%20revenue%20and%20almost%20%243%20billion%20of%20net%20earnings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman's%20investment%20banking%20fees%20soared%2020%25%20year-on-year%20to%20about%20%241.9%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20reported%20third-quarter%20earnings%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20beat%20Wall%20Street's%20expectations%2C%20sending%20its%20stock%20up%20as%20much%20as%203%25%20in%20premarket%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20bank%20generated%20%2412.7%20billion%20of%20net%20revenue%2C%20a%207%25%20increase%20from%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20It%20also%20cut%20its%20operating%20expenses%20by%208%25%2C%20fueling%20a%2045%25%20surge%20in%20net%20income%20to%20%242.99%20billion.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20per%20share%20were%20%248.40%2C%20exceeding%20Alphasense's%20consensus%20estimate%20of%20%246.71.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENet%20revenues%20rose%207%25%20year%20over%20year%20in%20the%20global%20banking%20and%20market%20division%2C%20fueled%20by%20a%2020%25%20jump%20in%20investment%20banking%20fees%20to%20%241.9%20billion.%20The%20fee%20bonanza%20reflected%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20net%20revenues%20from%20debt%20underwriting%20amid%20strong%20leveraged%20finance%20and%20investment-grade%20activity%2C%20and%20higher%20net%20revenues%20in%20equity%20underwriting%20driven%20by%20secondary%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20also%20benefited%20from%20an%2018%25%20rise%20in%20net%20revenues%20from%20its%20equities%20business%2C%20which%20helped%20offset%20a%2012%25%20drop%20in%20net%20revenues%20from%20the%20fixed%20income%2C%20currency%20and%20commodities%20(FICC)%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20asset%20and%20wealth%20management%20segment%20saw%20a%2016%25%20rise%20in%20net%20revenues%20as%20it%20collected%20record%20quarterly%20management%20and%20other%20fees.%20Moreover%2C%20assets%20under%20supervision%20grew%20by%20%24169%20billion%20last%20quarter%20to%20a%20record%20%243.1%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20David%20Solomon%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20release%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20performance%20demonstrates%20the%20strength%20of%20our%20world-class%20franchise%20in%20an%20improving%20operating%20environment.%20We%20continue%20to%20lean%20into%20our%20strengths%20%E2%80%93%20exceptional%20talent%2C%20execution%20capabilities%20and%20risk%20management%20expertise%20%E2%80%93%20allowing%20us%20to%20effectively%20serve%20our%20clients%20against%20a%20complex%20backdrop%20and%20deliver%20for%20shareholders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20struck%20a%20cautious%20tone%20at%20a%20Barclays%20conference%20in%20September%2C%20per%20a%20transcript%20provided%20by%20AlphaSense%2C%20warning%20that%20Goldman's%20trading%20unit%20was%20trending%2010%25%20lower%20than%20a%20year%20earlier%20largely%20due%20to%20fixed-income%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolomon%20had%20also%20warned%20of%20a%20roughly%20%24400%20million%20blow%20to%20pre-tax%20earnings%20from%20the%20bank%20shifting%20away%20from%20its%20credit%20card%20partnership%20with%20General%20Motors%20and%20selling%20its%20seller%20financing%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bank%20of%20America's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20showed%20its%20revenues%20were%20almost%20flat%20year%20on%20year%20at%20%2425.3%20billion.%20Higher%20non-interest%20expenses%20pushed%20its%20net%20income%20down%2012%25%20to%20%246.9%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECEO%20Brian%20Moynihan%20said%20it%20was%20another%20good%20quarter%20with%20%26quot%3Bsolid%20earnings%20results%2C%20delivering%20higher%20average%20loans%20and%20our%20fifth%20consecutive%20quarter%20of%20sequential%20average%20deposit%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBank%20of%20America%20stock%20was%20up%201.7%25%20in%20premarket%20trading%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-earnings-third-quarter-profits-banking-economy-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728992236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e3143a70318649281c751%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-earnings-third-quarter-profits-banking-economy-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Goldman%20Sachs%20reported%20third-quarter%20earnings%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20surpassed%20analysts'%20expectations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-earnings-third-quarter-profits-banking-economy-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Social%20media%20users%20label%20Kamala%20Harris%20a%20'con%20artist'%20after%20plagiarism%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728992100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fm