dominated%2C%20winning%20161%20of%20288%20seats.%20However%2C%20the%20alliance%20broke%20down%20over%20sharing%20of%20power%20and%20the%20Sena%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20government%2C%20however%2C%20lasted%20only%20till%202023%3B%20rebellions%20by%20the%20Sena's%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20now%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20-%20and%20the%20NCP's%20Ajit%20Pawar%20-%20now%20Mr%20Shinde's%20deputy%20-%20forced%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20to%20resign%20and%20his%20coalition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%20to%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2024%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20the%20BJP%20-%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20now%20with%20the%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20factions%20that%20broke%20away%20from%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20-%20will%20look%20to%20finish%202024%20on%20a%20high%20after%20a%20historic%20April-June%20general%20election%20that%20saw%20Narendra%20Modi%20become%20a%20three-time%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20will%20bank%20on%20his%20flagship%20scheme%20-%20%3Cem%3ELadki%20Bahin%20Yojana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%C2%A0sees%20poor%20women%20get%20a%20monthly%20stipend%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20-%20to%20sway%20voters%20after%20his%20alliance's%20poor%20show%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20alliance%20-%20dubbed%20Mahayuti%20-%20won%20just%2017%20of%20the%2048%20parliamentary%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rs%2046%2C000-crore%20a%20year%20welfare%20scheme%20has%20been%20hailed%20as%20a%20'game-changer'%2C%20quite%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3ELadli%20Behna%20Yogna%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0of%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20helped%20the%20BJP%20retain%20that%20state%20last%20year%20despite%2C%20again%2C%20anti-incumbency%20and%20widespread%20expectations%20of%20a%20Congress