e7cb008d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-final-frontier-life-on-europa-nasa-launch-jupiter-moon-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA's%20Europa%20Clipper%20launched%20on%20Monday%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20SpaceX%20Falcon%20Heavy%20rocket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-final-frontier-life-on-europa-nasa-launch-jupiter-moon-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20To%20Vote%20In%202%20Phases%20On%20November%2013%20and%2020%2C%20Results%20On%20November%2023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20year%20of%20elections%20is%20set%20to%20come%20to%20a%20close%20with%20the%20Jharkhand%20and%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20eastern%20state%20will%20vote%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20beginning%20November%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20phase%20of%20voting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20November%2020%20and%20the%20counting%20will%20take%20place%20on%20November%2023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20has%2081%20Assembly%20seats%2C%20with%2041%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20majority%2C%20and%202.6%20crore%20eligible%20voters.%20Polling%20was%20held%20in%20five%20phases%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20currently%20ruled%20by%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20which%20are%20also%20allies%20at%20the%20national%20level%20as%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20The%20alliance%20is%20hoping%20to%20form%20a%20government%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20time%20under%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20JMM%20had%20contested%2043%20seats%20and%20won%2030%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2016%20of%2031%20while%20the%20RJD%20managed%20to%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20only%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20constituencies%20it%20had%20put%20up%20candidates%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coalition%20faces%20a%20stiff%20challenge%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20for%20a%20term%20before%202019%20and%20is%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20Sudesh%20Mahto's%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi's%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(Secular)%20or%20HAM(S).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%20the%20LJP%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20and%20HAM%20(S)%20will%20be%20contesting%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20the%20biggest%20party%20is%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20won%2025%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20elections%20and%2037%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20had%20won%20nine%20of%20the%20state's%2014%20seats%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20got%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20big%20issues%20in%20this%20election%20is%20the%20arrest%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20January%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20land%20scam%20case.%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20June%20but%20his%20party%20got%20a%20jolt%20when%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20his%20absence%20and%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20JMM's%20number%20three%2C%20quit%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20said%20Champai%20Soren's%20entry%20into%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20help%20the%20party%20perform%20better%20in%20the%20state's%2028%20tribal%20constituencies%2C%20where%20the%20JMM%20has%20traditionally%20been%20strong%2C%20which%20will%20be%20critical%20in%20any%20alliance%20forming%20the%20government.%20Another%20factor%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20work%20in%20the%20BJP's%20favour%20is%20its%20surprise%20victory%20in%20Haryana%20after%2010%20years%20in%20power%2C%20which%20has%20enthused%20the%20state's%20cadre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Haryana%20results%2C%20the%20momentum%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20with%20the%20JMM-Congress%20alliance%20but%20a%20closer%20contest%20is%20expected%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20why%20the%20elections%20were%20being%20held%20in%20two%20phases%20in%20Jharkhand%20when%20Maharashtra%20is%20voting%20in%20a%20single%20phase%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20state%20faces%20security%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20presence%20of%20Maoists%2C%20and%20voting%20was%20conducted%20in%20five%20phases%20last%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728991200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Faq7kpjgc_evm-generic_625x300_21_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-will-vote-in-2-phases-on-nov-13-and-20-results-on-nov-23-6794323%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20year%20of%20elections%20is%20set%20to%20come%20to%20a%20close%20with%20the%20Jharkhand%20and%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20polls%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20eastern%20state%20will%20vote%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20beginning%20November%2013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-will-vote-in-2-phases-on-nov-13-and-20-results-on-nov-23-6794323%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ratan%20Tata's%20pet%20dog%20Goa%20dies%3A%20Mumbai%20Police%20inspector%20'clarifies'%20this%20viral%20post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728991177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114250150%2Cimgsize-26610.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%