0He%20starred%20with%20a%20century%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20of%20the%20recently-concluded%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Gill%20boasts%20the%20highest%20batting%20average%20among%20all%20Indian%20batsmen%20in%20Test%20cricket%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20-%20who%20slammed%20a%20stunning%20double%20century%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20Duleep%20Trophy%20-%20would%20be%20the%20favourite%20to%20replace%20Gill%20in%20the%20lineup.%20After%20a%20good%20start%20to%20his%20Test%20career%20against%20England%2C%20Sarfaraz%20could've%20considered%20himself%20a%20tad%20unlucky%20to%20miss%20out%20after%20the%20return%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20Sarfaraz%20does%20enter%20the%20XI%2C%20India's%20batting%20order%20may%20need%20to%20be%20re-shuffled.%20Who%20goes%20up%20to%20No.%203%20would%20be%20an%20interesting%20decision.%20India%20may%20opt%20to%20go%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20face%20New%20Zealand%20after%20a%20dominant%202-0%20Test%20series%20win%20over%20Bangladesh.%20History%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20India%2C%20as%20New%20Zealand%20have%20never%20won%20an%20away%20Test%20series%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20a%20result%20in%20the%20game%20is%20in%20doubt%2C%20with%20rain%20predicted%20to%20impact%20play%20o