22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-eyes-joe-rogan-podcast-to-win-over-young-male-voters%2Farticleshow%2F114243508.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-eyes-joe-rogan-podcast-to-win-over-young-male-voters%2Famp_articleshow%2F114243508.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkamala-harris-eyes-joe-rogan-podcast-to-win-over-young-male-voters%2Famp_articleshow%2F114243508.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20India's%20Rail%20Infrastructure%20On%20Life%20Support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERailway%20accidents%20have%20been%20in%20the%20headlines%20this%20year.%20In%20yet%20another%20signal%20failure%20accident%2C%20the%20Mysuru-Darbhanga%20Express%20rammed%20a%20stationary%20goods%20train%20at%20Kavarapettai%20in%20the%20Chennai%20Division%20of%20Southern%20Railway%20on%20October%2011%20night.%20More%20than%20two%20dozen%20people%20were%20injured.%20Two%20goods%20trains%20derailed%20in%20September%20--%20one%20in%20Mathura%2C%20another%20in%20Jharkhand.%20The%20Howrah-Mumbai%20Mail%20derailed%20following%20a%20collision%20with%20a%20goods%20train%20in%20Seraikela-Kharsawan%20district%20of%20Jharkhand%20on%20July%2030.%20The%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20travelling%20from%20Agartala%20to%20Sealdah%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20June%2017%20collided%20with%20a%20goods%20train%20near%20Rangapani%2C%20close%20to%20New%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20resulting%20in%2011%20deaths.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20in%20just%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20there%20were%2019%20train%20derailments%2C%20resulting%20in%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20351%20people%20have%20died%20and%20970%20injured%20in%20200%20consequential%20railway%20accidents%2C%20per%20data%20of%20Indian%20Railways%20from%20its%2017%20railway%20zones.%20Both%20passenger%20and%20goods%20trains%20were%20involved%20in%20these%20accidents%2C%20raising%20issues%20about%20the%20state%20of%20rail%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20obstructed%20the%20movement%20of%20other%20trains%20in%20the%20impacted%20sections%2C%20forcing%20railways%20to%20delay%20or%20divert%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chennai%20train%20accident%20is%20similar%20to%20the%202023%20Balasore%20train%20crash%2C%20in%20which%20three%20trains%20were%20involved.%20The%20Coromandel%20Express%20had%20similarly%20entered%20a%20loop%20line%2C%20struck%20a%20goods%20train%20and%20derailed%2C%20before%20another%20train%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-Howrah%20Superfast%2C%20crashed%20into%20it.%20With%20296%20people%20dead%20and%20many%20injured%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20train%20accidents%20in%20India's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Railways%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20busiest%20rail%20networks%20in%20the%20world%2C%20carrying%20lakhs%20of%20people%20and%20tonnes%20of%20goods%20daily.%20The%20accidents%20raise%20a%20big%20question%20on%20the%20mode%20of%20transport%20that%20crores%20of%20Indians%20rely%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutdated%20infra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20train%20derailments%20have%20occurred%20due%20to%20poor%20track%20maintenance%2C%20overcrowding%2C%20operational%20errors%2C%20outdated%20signalling%20systems%2C%20weather%20etc.%20Human%20errors%20like%20driver's%20exhaustion%20and%20carelessness%2C%20communication%20faults%2C%20and%20insufficient%20training%20have%20also%20emerged%20as%20key%20reasons%20for%20train%20accidents.%20Heavy%20rainfall%2C%20landslides%2C%20and%20floods%20also%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20train%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overcrowding%20and%20overloading%20of%20trains%20have%20exacerbated%20an%20already%20critical%20situation.%20Overcrowded%20trains%20place%20extra%20pressure%20on%20the%20tracks%20and%20rolling%20stock%2C%20making%20them%20more%20prone%20to%20accidents.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20overloading%20of%20goods%20trains%20beyond%20their%20capacity%20can%20lead%20to%20derailments%20due%20to%20the%20disproportionate%20weight%20and%20tension%20on%20the%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20total%20failure%20and%20non-adherence%20to%20strict%20standards%20of%20maintenance%20of%20rolling%20stocks%2C%20wagons%20and%20coaches%20by%20the%20railways%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20railway%20safety%20expert%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetting%20priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reduce%20accidents%2C%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20been%20developing%20and%20upgrading%20technology%20in%20signalling%20and%20telecommunication%2C%20with%20automatic%20signalling%20on%2015%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20network%20and%20plans%20for%20the%20KAVACH%20-%20the%20domestically%20developed%20Train%20Collision%20Avoidance%20System%20-%20to%20cover%2037%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks.%20However%2C%20these%20are%20still%20work%20in%20progress.%20Both%20the%20Chennai%20train%20accident%20and%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20crash%20could%20have%20been%20averted%20by%20installing%20Kavach%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20achieve%20zero%20accidents%20by%20preventing%20speeding%20or%20signal%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20deploying%20Kavach%20in%20the%20existing%20railway%20networks%20without%20disrupting%20train%20movement%20makes%20the%20task%20particularly%20challenging.%20%26quot%3BKavach%20can't%20save%20all%20collisions.%20Side%20track%20collisions%20can't%20be%20prevented%20by%20Kavach%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20retired%20railways%20official%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20that%20despite%20the%20increase%20in%20railways%20revenue%20in%20the%20Budget%2C%20the%20rail%20bureaucracy%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20utilise%20funds%20aiming%20for%20zero%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railways%20revenue%20in%202022-23%20was%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore%2C%20and%20the%20track%20renewal%20spending%20in%20that%20year%20was%2013.5%25%20of%20the%20revenue.%20In%20FY24%20(Revised%20Estimates)%2C%20the%20total%20railway%20revenue%20rose%20to%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%2C%20but%20spending%20on%20track%20renewal%20dropped%20to%2011%25%20of%20the%20revenue.%20In%20the%20July%20budget%2C%20the%20railways%20revenue%20was%20planned%20at%20Rs%201.8%20lakh%20crore%20in%20FY25%20(Budget%20Estimates)%2C%20and%20the%20track%20renewal%20spending%20was%20at%209.7%25%20of%20this%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCapacity%20augmentation%20hasn't%20helped.%20It%20has%20saturated%20the%20existing%20network%20to%20breaking%20point.%20The%20maintenance%20window%20is%20even%20less%2C%20with%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20too%20running%20on%20the%20same%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20Board%2C%20which%20oversees%20rail%20services%20in%20India%2C%20runs%20the%20whole%20infrastructure.%20India's%20railway%20network%20is%20recognised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world%20under%20a%20single%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccountability%20needs%20to%20be%20fixed%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20railway%20bureaucracy.%20There%20is%20no%20railway%20safety%20regulator%20for%20day-to-day%20maintenance%20except%20the%20Commission%20of%20Railway%20Safety%2C%20whose%20role%20is%20limited%20to%20holding%20accident%20inquiries%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20rail%20safety%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw's%20constant%20refrain%20that%20the%20figure%20of%20171%20accidents%20per%20year%20has%20come%20down%20to%2040%20accidents%20in%2010%20years%20is%20hardly%20reassuring%20to%20passengers%20worried%20about%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20is%20being%20spent%20in%20replacing%20or%20repairing%20outdated%20railroads%2C%20getting%20new%20trains%2C%20and%20tackling%20thousands%20of%20unattended%20railroad%20crossings.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20much%20more%20work%20to%20be%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728984960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fuvrm7dj8_mysurudarbhanga-express-train-accident_625x300_15_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-rail-safety-off-track-as-train-incidents-surge-6793663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%20two%20dozen%20people%20were%20injured%20when%20the%20Mysuru-Darbhanga%20Express%20rammed%20a%20stationary%20goods%20train%20at%20Kavarapettai%20in%20the%20Chennai%20Division%20of%20Southern%20Railway%20on%20October%2011.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-rail-safety-off-track-as-train-incidents-surge-6793663%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Baba%20Siddique%20Murder%20Suspect%20Was%20Questioned%20In%20Salman%20Khan%20Case%20And%20Let%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20suspects%20that%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20are%20looking%20for%20in%20the%20sensational%20murder%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20last%20week%20had%20also%20been%20questioned%20after%20the%20firing%20outside%20the%20residence%20of%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20in%20April%2C%20but%20was%20let%20off%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%2C%20in%20their%20investigation%2C%20Shubham%20Lonkar%20is%20emerging%20as%20one%20of%20the%20key%20conspirators%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Siddique%2C%20who%20was%20a%20three-time%20MLA%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20after%20the%20firing%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20residence%2C%20Galaxy%20Apartments%2C%20in%20Bandra%2C%20Lonkar%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20people%20who%20had%20been%20picked%20up%20for%20questioning.%20His%20name%20was%20allegedly%20taken%20by%20several%20people%20who%20had%20been%20interrogated%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20sources%20said%20Lonkar%20was%20accused%20of%20providing%20shelter%20to%20the%20suspects%20in%20the%20firing%20case%20but%20had%20to%20be%20let%20go%20because%20no%20strong%20evidence%20could%20be%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20told%20NDTV%20earlier%20that%20Lonkar%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Pravin%2C%20were%20two%20of%20the%20key%20conspirators%20in%20the%20Siddique%20murder%20and%20had%20enlisted%20two%20of%20the%20shooters%20-%20Dharamraj%20Kashyap%20and%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Gautam%20-%20in%20the%20plot.%20A%20note%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20on%20Sunday%20in%20which%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20took%20responsibility%20for%20Siddique's%20murder%20was%20also%20allegedly%20from%20Shubham%20Lonkar's%20account.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pravin%20was%20arrested%20from%20Pune%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20Shubham%20is%20still%20on%20the%20run.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20the%20Lonkar%20brothers%20were%20used%20by%20the%20police%20in%20court%20on%20Monday%20to%20state%20officially%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20could%20be%20behind%20Siddique's%20killing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarning%20Post%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Lonkar%20claimed%20that%20Siddique%20had%20been%20killed%20because%20he%20was%20linked%20to%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorist%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%2C%20was%20close%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20because%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Anuj%20Thapan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arrested%20suspects%20in%20the%20shooting%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%2C%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThapan%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20May%201%20inside%20the%20Mumbai%20Crime%20Branch%20lock-up.%20The%20police%20had%20said%20he%20died%20by%20suicide%20but%20his%20family%20had%20claimed%20he%20was%20tortured%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20any%20enmity%20with%20anyone%20but%20whoever%20helps%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20the%20Dawood%20gang%2C%20keep%20your%20accounts%20in%20order%20(%3Cem%3E'hisab-kitaab%20kar%20lena'%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%26quot%3B%20Lonkar%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%20in%20the%20Facebook%20post%2C%20whose%20authenticity%20is%20being%20verified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20has%20been%20tightened%20around%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20in%20Bandra%20as%20well%20as%20his%20farmhouse%20in%20Panvel%20near%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728984720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fkhsju54o_salman-khan-ani_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-murder-accused-shubham-lonkar-on-the-run-was-questioned-in-salman-khan-case-6793278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20suspects%20that%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20are%20looking%20for%20in%20the%20sensational%20murder%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20last%20week%20had%20also%20been%20questioned%20after%20the%20firing%20outside%20the%20house%20of%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20in%20April.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-murder-accused-shubham-lonkar-on-the-run-was-questioned-in-salman-khan-case-6793278%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20takes%20on%20Ambani%20over%20satellite%20spectrum%20allocation%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728984339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-10%2F14%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1728888422-9502.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https