Url%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Finally%20Reveals%20Why%20Bumrah%20Was%20Made%20Vice-Captain%20Of%20Test%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20made%20its%20preference%20clear%20as%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20New%20Zealand%20was%20announced.%20While%20Rohit%20Sharma%20remains%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%2C%20the%20BCCI%20selection%20committee%20officially%20put%20the%20vice-captain%20tag%20on%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20has%20been%20widely%20recognised%20as%20India's%20most%20important%20player%20at%20present.%20Though%20Bumrah%20doesn't%20have%20much%20captaincy%20experience%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20leadership%20group%20for%20a%20long%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Rohit%20was%20asked%20about%20Bumrah's%20leadership%2C%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20now%20officially%20been%20given%20the%20vice-captain's%20tag.%20The%20Hitman%20explained%20how%20much%20he%20has%20welcomed%20Bumrah's%20inputs%20during%20matches%2C%20even%20though%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20captaincy%20experience%20at%20any%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20Bumrah%20has%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20I've%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20with%20him.%20He%20understands%20the%20game%20pretty%20well.%20He's%20got%20a%20good%20head%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20When%20you%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20he%20understands%20the%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20told%20reporters%20during%20his%20pre-match%20press%20meet%20after%20rain%20hampered%20India's%20training%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTactically%2C%20I%20can't%20say%20much%20because%20he%20has%20not%20captained%20much.%20He%20was%20captain%20in%20one%20Test%20match%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20T20s%2C%20I%20guess%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20understands%20what%20is%20required.%20When%20you%20are%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20you%20need%20a%20leader%20to%20step%20up%2C%20I%20think%20Bumrah%20will%20be%20one%20of%20them.%20So%2C%20over%20the%20past%2C%20he's%20always%20been%20in%20our%20leadership%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20the%20most%20experienced%20pacer%20in%20the%20team%2C%20Bumrah%20has%20also%20been%20tasked%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20helping%20young%20pacers%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20speaking%20to%20the%20bowlers%20who%20have%20just%20come%20into%20the%20squad%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20getting%20internally%20with%20the%20team%20to%20discuss%20about%20how%20to%20move%20forward%20as%20a%20team%2C%20he's%20always%20been%20part%20of%20that%20leadership%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20it's%20probably%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20just%20have%20him%20around%20and%20speak%20to%20the%20bowlers%20and%20internally%20discuss%20how%20to%20take%20the%20team%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Rohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20potential%20return%20of%20Bumrah's%20pace%20bowling%20partner%20Mohammed%20Shami.%20The%20India%20skipper%20all%20but%20ruled%20out%20Shami's%20inclusion%20for%20the%20Australia%20tour%2C%20suggesting%20the%20veteran%20speedster%20remains%20undercooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20right%20now%2C%20it's%20pretty%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20make%20a%20call%20on%20him%2C%20whether%20he'll%20be%20fit%20for%20this%20series%20or%20the%20Australia%20series.%20He%20recently%20had%20swelling%20on%20his%20knee%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20unusual%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20fit%2C%20getting%20close%20to%20100%20percent%2C%20he%20had%20swelling%20in%20his%20knee%2C%20that%20put%20him%20back%20a%20little%20bit%20in%20his%20recovery.%20So%2C%20he%20had%20to%20start%20again.%20Right%20now%2C%20he's%20at%20NCA%2C%20he's%20working%20with%20the%20physios%20and%20the%20doctors%20at%20NCA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728982080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fdi2pd5o_rohit-sharma-and-jasprit-bumrah-bcci_625x300_15_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Frohit-sharmas-verdict-on-vice-captain-jasprit-bumrah-settles-all-captaincy-questions-6792940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%20was%20officially%20named%20Team%20India's%20vice-captain%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20New%20Zealand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Frohit-sharmas-verdict-on-vice-captain-jasprit-bumrah-settles-all-captaincy-questions-6792940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citadel%3A%20Honey%20Bunny's%20action%20packed%20trailer%20launched%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728981813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114242699%2Cimgsize-52254.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fcitadel-honey-bunny-trailer-varun-dhawan-and-samantha-channel-their-inner-james-bond-for-this-90s-themed-action-series-teases-priyanka-chopras-character-connection%2Farticleshow%2F114242138.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114242138.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E'Citadel%3A%20Honey%20Bunny'%2C%20the%20Indian%20spin-off%20of%20the%20global%20franchise%2C%20stars%20Varun%20Dhawan%20and%20Samantha%20Akkineni%20as%20protagonists%20in%20a%2090s%20espionage%20setting.%20Directed%20by%20Raj%20and%20DK%2C%20the%20series%20unveils%20their%20tumultuous%20past%20and%20connections%20with%