here%20had%20been%20a%20lull%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20some%20gangs%20from%20north%20India%2C%20like%20the%20one%20led%20by%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20capitalise%20on%20this%20vacuum.%20The%20murder%20of%20Baba%20Siddique%20is%20perhaps%20a%20manifestation%20of%20this%20emerging%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUneasy%20Flashbacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddique's%20murder%20on%20Sunday%20has%20triggered%20fears%20that%20Mumbai%20may%20be%20reverting%20to%20the%20dreaded%20days%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20when%20bloodshed%20on%20the%20streets%20was%20rampant.%20Gangsters%20not%20only%20killed%20their%20rivals%20but%20also%20targeted%20bar%20owners%2C%20builders%2C%20film%20producers%2C%20and%20various%20businessmen%20who%20refused%20to%20pay%20extortion%20money.%20Over%20a%20hundred%20people%20were%20killed%20every%20year%20in%20that%20decade.%20The%20lawlessness%20in%20India's%20financial%20capital%20made%20national%20headlines%20especially%20when%20audacious%20gangsters%20killed%20a%20businessman%20right%20outside%20the%20police%20commissioner's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20adopted%20strict%20measures%20to%20combat%20the%20mafia's%20reign%20of%20terror%2C%20including%20the%20controversial%20policy%20of%20encounters.%20Around%20500%20gangsters%20were%20killed%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20'90s%2C%20and%20thousands%20were%20arrested%20under%20the%20stringent%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organized%20Crime%20Act.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20underworld%20by%20the%20time%20the%2021st%20century%20completed%20its%20first%20decade.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnDawood%20Ibrahim%20wound%20up%20his%20gang's%20operations%20in%20India%20after%20his%20younger%20brother%20Iqbal%20was%20deported%20from%20Dubai%20in%202003.%20Gawli%2C%20Rajan%2C%20and%20Abu%20Salem%20are%20serving%20life%20sentences%20in%20various%20murder%20cases.%20Even%20small-time%20gangsters%20like%20Ravi%20Pujari%20and%20Bunty%20Pandey%20are%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Threats%20To%20Salman%20Khan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitial%20investigations%20into%20the%20Baba%20Siddique%20murder%20case%20suggest%20that%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20could%20be%20behind%20the%20killing.%20Although%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20conclusively%20established%20that%20the%20incarcerated%20gangster%20ordered%20the%20hit%2C%20it%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20was%20on%20his%20hit%20list.%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20had%20made%20two%20unsuccessful%20attempts%20to%20eliminate%20him.%20When%20they%20couldn't%20succeed%20in%20killing%20Khan%2C%20they%20fired%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Bandra%20to%20intimidate%20him.%20Bishnoi%20seems%20to%20have%20followed%20the%20old%20underworld%20formula%20that%20if%20you%20can't%20kill%20your%20enemy%2C%20kill%20his%20acquaintances%20or%20destroy%20his%20support%20system.%20Baba%20Siddique%20was%20not%20just%20Khan's%20friend%20but%20also%20one%20of%20his%20support%20pillars%2C%20standing%20by%20him%20through%20tough%20times%20like%20the%20hit-and-run%20case%20and%20the%20blackbuck%20hunting%20case.%20It%20could%20be%20surmised%20that%20Bishnoi%20targeted%20Siddique%20to%20intimidate%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Siddique%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20like%20many%20others%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20he%20had%20a%20few%20enemies.%20The%20police%20are%20also%20investigating%20the%20possibility%20of%20business%20rivalry%20being%20a%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20Of%20'Nationalist'%20Gangsters%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20Siddique%20was%20shot%20dead%2C%20someone%20came%20forward%20on%20social%20media%20to%20claim%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack.%20The%20post%20warned%20others%20who%20were%20friendly%20with%20Khan%20that%20they%20could%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20Siddique's.%20The%20post%20ended%20with%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BJai%20Shri%20Ram%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BJai%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%20Such%20slogans%20suggest%20that%20Bishnoi%20wants%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20Hindu%20don%2C%20not%20just%20an%20avenger%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20community.%20This%20mirrors%20strategies%20used%20by%20Mumbai%20underworld%20mafias.%20The%20Chhota%20Rajan%20gang%2C%20by%20killing%20those%20accused%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20serial%20bombings%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Pujari%2C%20by%20threatening%20defence%20lawyers%20in%20terror%20cases%20and%20left-leaning%20celebrities%20like%20Mahesh%20Bhatt%2C%20had%20also%20sought%20to%20project%20themselves%20as%20nationalist%20gangsters%2C%20not%20just%20money-driven%20criminals.%20Similarly%2C%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20tried%20to%20garner%20support%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20by%20orchestrating%20the%20Mumbai%20serial%20blasts%2C%20which%20were%20touted%20as%20revenge%20for%20the%20killings%20of%20Muslims%20during%20the%20Mumbai%20riots.%20The%20gang%20also%20attacked%20Shiv%20Sainiks%2C%20who%20were%20indicted%20by%20the%20B.N.%20Srikrishna%20Commission%20for%20participating%20in%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20just%20two%20incidents%20in%20Mumbai.%20If%20more%20such%20incidents%20continue%20and%20Bishnoi%20tries%20to%20profit%20from%20terror%20by%20making%20extortion%20calls%20to%20the%20rich%20and%20wealthy%20in%20the%20city%2C%20then%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20will%20need%20to%20brace%20for%20another%20war%20against%20the%20underworld.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20challenge%20will%20be%20different%2C%20as%2C%20unlike%20the%20gangsters%20of%20the%20'90s%2C%20the%20members%20of%20Bishnoi's%20gang%20hail%20from%20various%20North%20Indian%20states%2C%20are%20new%20to%20the%20crime%20world%2C%20and%20have%20a%20sparse%20criminal%20background.%20Most%20of%20the%20officers%20who%20fought%20the%20underworld%20in%20the%20'90s%20have%20retired.%20The%20new%20breed%20of%20Mumbai%20cops%20lacks%20the%20experience%20and%20expertise%20to%20deal%20with%20organised%20crime%20syndicates%2C%20and%20it%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20develop%20a%20network%20of%20informers%2C%20given%20that%20the%20gangsters%20are%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jitendra%20Dixit%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%20of%20NDTV%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20'Bombay%20After%20Ayodhya')%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728978120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fi4gtm5b_baba-siddiqui_625x300_15_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fshootout-at-bandra-baba-siddiques-murder-and-mumbais-dark-mafia-past-6792879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22So%20far%2C%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20two%20incidents%20in%20Mumbai.%20If%20Bishnoi%20tries%20to%20profit%20from%20terror%20by%20making%20extortion%20calls%20to%20the%20rich%2C%20then%20the%20Police%20will%20need%20to%20brace%20for%20another%20war%20against%20the%20underworld.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fshootout-at-bandra-baba-siddiques-murder-and-mumbais-dark-mafia-past-6792879%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Ash-Abhishek%20posed%20with%20SRK%2C%20Katrina%2C%20others%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728977736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114241324%2Cimgsize-65638.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-aishwarya-rai-abhishek-bachchan-posed-with-shah-rukh-khan-sridevi-katrina-kaif-sushant-singh-rajput-and-ot