%20in%20these%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInducing%20celebrity%20culture%20to%20reclaim%20public%20spaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20element%20of%20reclaiming%20these%20public%20spaces%20for%20women%20was%20through%20inducing%20celebrity%20culture%2C%20and%20they%20had%20the%20perfect%20candidate%20to%20lead%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cecelia%2C%20the%20local%20celebrity.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIndu-Antony-Cecelia-Image-1728656948-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-370029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECecelia%2C%20the%20local%20celebrity.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1Dg8HUuU8eU%26t%3D907s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETEDx%20Talk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Indu%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Cecelia%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20she%20was%20already%20a%20celebrity.%20She%20had%20this%20eclectic%20sense%20of%20fa