0go%20to%20a%20doctor.%20Find%20one%20who%20listens%20to%20you%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up.%20Start%20taking%20care%20of%20yourself%20and%20give%20priority%20to%20your%20own%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728564604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D369628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Devleena%20Chatterjee%20and%20Sneha%20Khedkar%20share%20their%20stories%20of%20living%20with%20debilitating%20pain%20every%20month.%20Doctors%20sent%20them%20home%20with%20painkillers%20saying%20that%20they%20had%20a%20lower%20tolerance%20for%20pain.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20finally%20got%20an%20answer%20through%20an%20endometriosis%20diagnosis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369628%2Fendometriosis-gynaecologists-womens-health-pain-periods-menstrual-cramps-devleena-chatterjee-sneha-khedkar%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Breaking%20News%20to%20Breaking%20Point%3A%20How%20a%20Journalist%20Uncovered%20an%20Anxiety%20Disorder%20Through%20Ear%20Pain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Representational%20Image%20above%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20constant%20feeling%20of%20darkness%20inside%20and%20outside%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202024%2C%20Rama%20started%20experiencing%20pain%20in%20her%20ears%2C%20a%20constant%20sensation%20of%20discomfort%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20overlook.%20This%20kicked%20off%20a%20series%20of%20visits%20to%20Ear%2C%20Nose%2C%20and%20Throat%20(ENT)%20specialists.%20Even%20after%20surgery%2C%20she%20had%20a%20gnawing%20feeling%20that%20something%20was%20still%20wrong%2C%20which%20led%20her%20to%20continue%20visiting%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20ti