cing%20a%20demanding%20job%20at%20a%20book-binding%20company%20and%20caring%20for%20her%20two%20daughters.%20While%20she%20was%20pushed%20to%20her%20limits%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally%2C%20the%20violence%20at%20home%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20eight%20years%20until%20one%20day%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20him%20to%20pay%20at%20least%20for%20the%20groceries%2C%20but%20he%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20cried%20myself%20to%20sleep%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20day%2C%20he%20again%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20was%20exhausted%20of%20this%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ambika%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20was%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20end%20her%20suffering%20by%20taking%20her%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20poured%20some%20kerosene%20on%20me%20and%20set%20myself%20on%20fire.%20When%20my%20neighbours%20saw%20me%20burn%2C%20I%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital.%20I%20sustained%2034%20percent%20burn%20injuries%20on%20my%20body.%20The%20scars%20were%20deep.%20Even%20now%20I%20have%20burn%20marks%20on%20my%20right%20parts%20of%20the%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20Ambika%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20suffering%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268203%2Fteen-fights-domestic-violence-breakthrough-india-nargis-covid-lockdown-dhakal-do-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20domestic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20just%20one%20among%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20violence%20often%20results%20in%20severe%20injuries%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20dislocations%2C%20burns%2C%20deep%20wounds%2C%20and%20broken%20teeth%20or%20bones.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1728394787-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369241%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20violence%20often%20results%20in%20severe%20injuries%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20dislocations%2C%20burns%2C%20deep%20wounds%2C%20and%20broken%20teeth%20or%20bones.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%20(NFHS-5)%2C%20one%20in%20three%20ever-married%20women%20in%20India%20experiences%20physical%2C%20sexual%2C%20or%20emotional%20abuse%20from%20their%20husbands%20during%20their%20lifetime.%20The%20violence%20often%20results%20in%20severe%20injuries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20eye%20trauma%2C%20sprains%2C%20dislocations%2C%20burns%2C%20deep%20wounds%2C%20and%20broken%20teeth%20or%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20horrifying%20cruelty%2C%20many%20cases%20go%20unreported%2C%20with%20only%2014%20percent%20of%20women%20seeking%20help%20to%20stop%20the%20abuse.%20A%20majority%20of%20women%20are%20discouraged%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F229759%2Fips-hero-lockdown-abuse-call-helpline-raipur-domestic-violence-cases-inspiring-unsung-hero-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%20such%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22w