domestic%20violence.%20In%20contrast%2C%20India%20lacks%20adequate%20support%20services%2C%20including%20shelters%2C%20counselling%2C%20and%20legal%20aid%20for%20survivors%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20high%20time%20we%20rethink%20our%20society%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20well-being.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20(left)%20founded%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Victim%20Care%20to%20assist%20survivors%20of%20domestic%20violence.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20(left)%20founded%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Victim%20Care%20to%20assist%20survivors%20of%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202001%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20start%20an%20organisation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Victim%20Care%20%E2%80%93%20dedicated%20to%20wome